text: Dutch Flat (also, Dutchman's Flat, Dutch Charlie's Flat, and Charley's Flat) is a small unincorporated community and census-designated place (CDP) in Placer County, California, United States, about northeast of Auburn along Interstate 80. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in California Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in Placer County, California Category:California Historical Landmarks
title: Dutch Flat, California
